{
  "stem": "6837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to give your jewelry and whatever you possessed-- your-- the women, their marriage bands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had earrings and a watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to give it to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were there some soldiers and police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was some Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They occupied, but they didn't bear the Nazi uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just wore regular German uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, then we went back home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- of course we were sad that we had to give in what was-- you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't bother us so much, because we were more concerned what else?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's-- what's going to be next?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What will they do to us next?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they came, and they told us that we'll have to gather the most necessary belongings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some soldiers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have to stay outside, line up front of the house and wait till the turn's going to be that we should-- we'll have to walk to the station.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in May.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The beginning of May '44, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The most necessary, like we had some food leftover, a change of clothing, and for the babies, the children's clothing and blankets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to carry it ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a children's carriage, which we piled up on there whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we walked to the station with our neighbors whoever was-- and by this station, the cattle cars were waiting, and they crammed us in there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, um, that they, um, take animals in, like cattles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no chairs, no nothing, just the floor-- bare floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to squeeze in because it was very crowded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us 80 people into one cattle car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the family, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were together-- my father, my mother and my brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
